&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Peppa&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;you-must-wear-your-boots-1&#34;&gt;George. If you jump in muddy puddles
you must wear your boots.
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;George&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
